          <div property="content:encoded" class="field-item even"><p>I got the chance a while back to speak with Amitai Burstein, CTO of <a href="http://www.gizra.com/">Gizra</a> - a boutique development shop in Tel Aviv creating advanced web applications using Drupal, along with Node.js, Jekyll and other technologies. Amitai is the maintainer of key Drupal modules such as Organic Groups, Message and Entity Reference, and contributes to Drupal core. He showed off Gizra's intriguing solution to content deployment in Drupal in this jam's Drupal Camp session: Zariz. I was impressed! You might be, too.</p>
